About us

Our Mission 

Our mission is to provide a healthy fresh and home made snacks with high quality ,hygiene and in affordable prices.

Our Story

Based in Satna, Madhya Pradesh, our snacks brand specializes in ready-to-fry chips, papads, and ready-to-serve snacks. We prioritize quality and flavor to enrich snacking experiences. Our varied offerings include banana chips, chivda, murmura, and namak para, ensuring there's something for everyone.

"Swad Ki Ye Kahani, Rasoiyaa Se Aap Tak"

"Rasoiyaa ek chhoti si soch se shuru hua tha – ghar jaisa swad sab tak pahunchane ka sapna. Aaj hum har snack ke saath wahi ghar ka pyaar, purity aur flavour aapke ghar tak le aate hain. Ye sirf snack nahi, ek experience hai jo har din ko special banata hai."
